Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:37.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的春天！寂寞的妖精物语！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东风逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年中最寒冷的季节到来时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被空虚弄锈的声音又再响起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原被视为当然的一切事物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然被认为是一件偶发的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都想丢弃的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 似乎身心中都浸在冬天一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly me to the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and let me play among the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see what spring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is like on Jupiter and Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 诸星当
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然感到这种心情的早晨到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这原因是昨晚和拉姆的些微争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哦 别在上课感伤好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see what spring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is like on Jupiter and Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何这种日子有体育课
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不好玩的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何在这么冷的日子做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当当奖励用工具互欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却高喊反对战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本民族根本的意识到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伪善
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何只因拉姆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遭受这无聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本应有的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是与更多更凉快的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种事 那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来这样的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 交手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8号 少女A（A级不良少女）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿当发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是阿当花心什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好的时间 达令把它弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令自己讲5点的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却在4点的时候等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被怪罪迟到一小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是阿当的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都安排到自己绝对是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能向他道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要彻底冷淡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然任由他去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去反省自己的自私才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的两位讲完了没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 玩弄招术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就逃跑而言真是绝妙的腿功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十六计走为上策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是兵法之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能逃到哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要等一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4点10分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆那小子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险\N但也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那衣服 脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么惨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸？！原来就这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在公园做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令真早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看嘛 和达令的衣服是一对的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为找这件衣服 花了不少工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令的衣服湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要等上一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但达令不是说5点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想听借口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概没问题所以没担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你是被面堂及眼镜他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扛回来的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没和他们一起回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没吃中饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要热一下便当
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 没事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打的地方是否有问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…确实…不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这和你相会 真是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字 电话 住址告知一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么看我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是既透彻又大的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在哪里？出来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有地方想和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？儿童乐园吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是你家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到明天就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚到底晃到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈你真落伍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和喜欢躲迷藏的女孩约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？头不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪下得越来越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下明天是银色的约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令在生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对白天不管达令的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 快准备吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what spring is like on Jupiter and Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In another words, hold my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否客气一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉没考虑到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您渴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如此 今天有银色的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是牛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当做牛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我认真扫地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种下法似乎不太正常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我们无法想象的神秘力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在控制着这场雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还没到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不会像拉姆迟到一…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚来 刚来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这天气还特地为我跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 又那么一幅脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的脸虽然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看看你的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太会笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样也非常不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而想和我去的地方是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去的地方 我哪都去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 你知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关冬之国妖精的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之国的妖精？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 控制风雪的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候会经读过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有心中被冬天侵入之时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这时候又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊或想到别的世界去之时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这妖精便出现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他带到冬之国
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后到了冬之过的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去过去快乐的记忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静静地 无征兆地冬之妖精便到来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被悲伤套住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没发觉任何事物时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头一看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从背后传来如冰冻的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:16:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐…渐渐变大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到底要到哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个非常美的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰的城堡屋顶上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整片的闪亮着飘着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常 非常美的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像蛮冷的地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要带个暖炉 怀炉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要去冬之国了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再也回不到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快的记忆将全部忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要等上一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听什么借口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也要放任他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他反省他自己的自私才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女朋友吵架你的心飘离了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的事物都变得无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那心中的低气压
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冬之国的雷达扫描到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以为迎接你 我被派来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有牛丼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有穿泳装的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我要到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不要也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妖精的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要开这玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一下嘛 这是玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:19:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道什么叫“笑”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说能转世为别的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的妖精？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就不用带我走了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你一人是办不到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人之力是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要取走你的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之国就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越空间 超越时间的国度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能超越时间就好了 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越时间 只是4点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是等的时间很长嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么就5点好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5、5点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 拉姆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆一直在2楼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想睡就躺着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 她能微笑之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之妖精能转生为春之妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个罗曼蒂克的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.17,0:23:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的梦想的一群
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花吃的梦之果实中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我和达令爱之日子的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.42,0:23:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为从每晚由樱花梦中出现的达令保护樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.98,0:24:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和樱花 达令前往梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.87,0:24:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往梦中！争夺达令的究极战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========注===========
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.08,zhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不要」音似「妖精」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:10.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 我能说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:13.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感触是否能传达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:16.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:18.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:23.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:36.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的手所拥在怀里 在耳边轻声细语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:50.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远都不要离开我 我会给你个甜美的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:55.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请感受我 请了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:59.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我揽在你的臂弯里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:03.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你对我轻轻地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.39,0:01:06.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将日日夜夜爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:12.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人比我更爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱是如此真诚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:17.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:20.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否爱我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:25.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:30.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将银轮偷偷交给你 这是只有你一人的邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.81,0:24:36.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尝试保有它 是我小小的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.51,0:24:42.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定在今日 只有两人的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.29,0:24:49.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是公开的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.27,0:24:53.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将准备庆贺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.15,0:24:57.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！宝贝 给你个讯息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.85,0:25:01.40,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将献上所有的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.84,0:25:05.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.81,0:25:09.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你早些感受我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.73,0:25:12.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来！给我些诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.49,0:25:17.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要我如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.57,0:25:20.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请常来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.19,0:25:23.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将表示我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.36,0:25:28.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我和你在一起时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.00,0:25:31.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如何的美好

